<h3>How To Use The Targets</h3>
<p>Set the targets before launch, not after. Score against them every 30 days. If 4 of 6 are below target, the asset needs work. The most common fixes: shorten the flow, sharpen the result page, or push more traffic.</p>
<h3>Attribution Beyond The First Conversion</h3>
<p>The first conversion is the easy part. The harder part is tracking what happens after. Did the lead become an opportunity? Did the opportunity close? Did the customer expand?</p>
<p>Wire the data to the CRM with a clear UTM and source field. Track the cohort over 90 days. Compare against leads who came through static content. The lift in long-term value is usually 2 to 3x.</p>
